   <p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
   <p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: 1px; text-align: justify; line-height: 23.2727px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><a href="http://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzA5NTk0NzgwNA==&amp;mid=2452808647&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=29990a7098fce8d96cacbdb405b8475c&amp;chksm=8771deb4b00657a21ff068d9a3413ee8fe5241001983bba8c79e95463336a4d93f64815a3c67&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect" target="_blank" data_ue_src="http://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzA5NTk0NzgwNA==&amp;mid=2452808647&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=29990a7098fce8d96cacbdb405b8475c&amp;chksm=8771deb4b00657a21ff068d9a3413ee8fe5241001983bba8c79e95463336a4d93f64815a3c67&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect" style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="max-width: 100%; color: rgb(2, 30, 170); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">1、同城生意人，帮主有话说！</span></strong></a></p>
   <p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: 1px; text-align: justify; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
   <p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: 1px; text-align: justify; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><a href="http://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzA5NTk0NzgwNA==&amp;mid=2452808675&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=e61343842757cdc15304bac2ec4774e9&amp;chksm=8771de90b00657865a2a9d1289c5c09b3ac3e335ab3b14ab5ccef70b0b17e0b56725d194846d&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect" target="_blank" data_ue_src="http://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzA5NTk0NzgwNA==&amp;mid=2452808675&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=e61343842757cdc15304bac2ec4774e9&amp;chksm=8771de90b00657865a2a9d1289c5c09b3ac3e335ab3b14ab5ccef70b0b17e0b56725d194846d&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect" style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="max-width: 100%; color: rgb(2, 30, 170); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">2、生意人在长沙联盟已成立，欢迎长沙生意人加入！</span></strong></a></p>
   <p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: 1px; text-align: justify; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
